trans-unit.source:
There is no model '{0}' registered with the model attribute, so the ViewModelToModel attribute on property '{1}' is invalid.
Make sure that the property is a Catel property, not a regular property.
If you are sure that you have a model with this name, make sure it's public instead of private or protected for UWP because non-public reflection is not allowed in UWP.
trans-unit.target:
There is no model '{0}' registered with the model attribute, so the ViewModelToModel attribute on property '{1}' is invalid.
Make sure that the property is a Catel property, not a regular property.
If you are sure that you have a model with this name, make sure it's public instead of private or protected for UWP because non-public reflection is not allowed in UWP.
trans-unit.note: {0} = model name {1} = property that points to the model
